Build from source

 * Requirements

To build QRemoteSignal you need to have:
1. Qt 5.0.0 library or later
2. QJson-qt5 library (optional)
3. cmake
4. help2man utility (optional)
4. Doxygen utility (optional)

 * Build

On Unix-like systems go to the sources directory and run:

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make

On windows you can use cmake-gui to configure project

 * Install

After you've build the library run:

$ make install

to install it.

 * Build documentation

Just enable QRS_DOCS cmake option:

$ cmake -DQRS_DOCS=On ..
